---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Domain Discoverer" description="We respect your privacy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect information, and how to contact us.">
  <section class="container-pad">
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>We take privacy seriously. This policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and your choices. If you have questions, please contact us.</p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>DomainDiscoverer.com helps visitors discover valuable domain names. You can check availability and explore curated tools that support research. We aim to collect only what’s necessary for the site to function.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email address</strong> if you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us via a form powered by Netlify Forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Basic logs</strong> from our hosting provider (Netlify) for security and performance (for example, IP address, user agent, and timestamps).</li>
        <li><strong>Function requests</strong> such as domain availability checks. We do not store the domain queries you enter.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send the newsletter or replies you requested</li>
        <li>To maintain and improve site reliability</li>
        <li>To respond when you contact us</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Email and Unsubscribe</h2>
      <p>We only email people who opt in. Every message includes an unsubscribe link or clear directions to opt out. You can also contact us to be removed.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use functional cookies to keep the site running (for example, remembering consent). You can manage cookies in your browser.</p>

      <h2>Third‑Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use Netlify for hosting and forms processing. When you use third‑party links (e.g., to tools or registrars), their policies apply. We recommend that you review them before proceeding.</p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>We use modern hosting and sensible practices to protect data. No method is perfect, so please contact us if you find any issue.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We keep personal data only as long as necessary to provide the requested service or fulfill legal obligations. You may request deletion of your newsletter address or form submission.</p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Unsubscribe from emails at any time</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your newsletter address or form submission</li>
        <li>Control cookies in your browser</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy. The latest version is posted on this page. If changes are important, we’ll note that clearly.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy requests, use our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. We respond as quickly as possible.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
